  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK854">
<l>iṉpattu ḷiṉpam payakku mika leṉṉun</l>
<l>tuṉpattuṭ ṭuṉpaṅ keṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If hatred which is the greatest misery is destroyed, it will yield the greatest delight.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
